title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Fantasy 5' game
maintext:
SACRAMENTO (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the California Lottery’s “Fantasy 5” game were:
03-07-10-17-37
(three, seven, ten, seventeen, thirty-seven)
Estimated jackpot: $163,000
¶ The numbers are listed in sequential order, but any combination wins.
